metadata.title: Gulf of Alaska CTD Data (1974 - 1977)

creators.name: Atmospheric Research (OAR), Pacific Marine Environmental Laboratory (PMEL)

metadata.description:
CTD data were collected using Plessy CTD's, during the years 1974 to 1977.  Data are averaged to one meter records.  These data are stored on 6,793 disk files (41.6MB), and most of these were collected as part of the FOX and FOCI projects.
NOAAServer Codes: [L 75 50 -130 -180] ; nodateline
